{
  "stem": "24625.2",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my name is Na-- my father-- my name is Nathan Wunderman, and I-- and I live there and there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm married, and I have children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So everybody was registered as Jews, so they knew-- in case they wanted to get us together-- they knew where to find us, you see?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because in Belgium, you have to register where you live in the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "City hall, they have an address.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They always can find you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whenever you move, you have to a following address.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You have to re-register.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But during the war, they have to register all Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father did not go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, if they have to find me, let them find me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I'm not going to go in to tell them where I am.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the people say, hey, they're going to go, and they're going to take you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said, so what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At least they don't know I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have a chance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And don't go, either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was telling the other people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But they went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They registered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They wouldn't listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And my father, on account of this, had a good chance during the war because we had identity papers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it was marked on the paper, born Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The other people was marked, born Poland, Jew-- a big stamp on their card.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You follow me?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So they didn't have no paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They had to go false identities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But my father went on the same papers the whole war-- also Polish guy, but not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And that's the way he survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "For this, he was smart.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But he went through the first war, and he was not a youngster, my father.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he had more experience what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He lived-- in his young years, he went to-- he lived in Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
